NAME
       ballerina-version - Print the Ballerina version

SYNOPSIS
       bal [-v | version]


DESCRIPTION
       Print the Ballerina distribution version and the supported
       language specification version.

       Note: The 'bal -v' and 'bal --version' commands are
       identical to 'bal version'.


OPTIONS
       -v, -version
           Shorthand syntax for 'bal version'.
